academy that is under the general supervision of the commissioner of general services.
All fees collected must be deposited into a designated fund and used exclusively for the
administration, maintenance, and enhancement of such training academy.
SECTION 3. Tennessee Code Annotated, Section 38-8-203, is amended by adding the
following as a new subsection:
(c) The academy may sell goods that support the educational and operational
needs of the academy and promotional items.
SECTION 4. This act takes effect upon becoming law, the public welfare requiring it.
